OL,3,CNew species of beetle named after
OL,4,Cconservationist Gerald Durrell
OL,6,FA museum scientist has dedicated a new
OL,7,Fspecies of Madagascan beetle to Gerald
OL,8,FDurrell on his centenary year.
OL,10,FThe Macratria Durelli was named by
OL,11,FDmitry Telnov, who says Durrell's
OL,12,Fadventures in West Africa and South
OL,13,FAmerica inspired him to become a
OL,14,Fresearcher.
OL,16,FThe new species belongs to the genus
OL,17,FMacratria, a large group of beetles
OL,18,Fcomprising over 320 species.
