OL,3,CNew species of beetle named after
OL,4,Cconservationist Gerald Durrell
OL,6,FDmitry has described almost half of
OL,7,Fthese beetles, giving official names
OL,8,Fto over 150 species in this group
OL,9,Falone.
OL,11,FThey are found on every continent
OL,12,Fexcept Antarctica, but mainly live
OL,13,Fnear the tropics, according to the
OL,14,FNatural History Museum.
OL,16,FDmitry Telnov, now an expert in
OL,17,Fbeetles, said: "Gerald Durrell has
OL,18,Fbeen a huge inspiration to me
OL,19,Fthroughout my life.
