OL,3,CNew species of beetle named after
OL,4,Cconservationist Gerald Durrell
OL,6,F"He helped me realise, as a scientist,
OL,7,Fthat we have to use our knowledge to
OL,8,Fhelp conserve nature and not just
OL,9,Fstudy it.
OL,11,F"This new species of beetle is from
OL,12,FMadagascar, a country where Gerald
OL,13,Fworked for a long time. It was part of
OL,14,Fhis work here that made him realise
OL,15,Fthat species were disappearing and we
OL,16,Fhad to do something about it.
OL,18,F"This year also marks 100 years since
OL,19,Fthe birth of Gerald Durrell, so I felt
OL,20,Fit was a perfect time to honour his
OL,21,Fextraordinary legacy."
